com.hotels.styx.api.extension.loadbalancing.spi

Interface LoadBalancer.Preferences

  • Enclosing interface:
    LoadBalancer

    public static interface LoadBalancer.Preferences
    Preferences requested from the load balancer. Consumer may ask load balancer to prefer some hosts over others by using the preferences object. Load balancer is under no obligation to actually satisfy these requirements. Instead, load balancer may choose to ignore them. It is at its own discretion if the preferences are honoured.
